      "content": "Engine, I'm reading the telemetry from the high-gain antenna, and I concur that the secondary sensor reading is a significant discovery. Investigating this thermal anomaly could yield valuable insights into the Martian geology and potentially alter our understanding of the planet's habitability. I recommend re-routing power to the surface suite to conduct a targeted survey of the anomaly, rather than entering Low Power Mode. This will allow us to gather more data and potentially extend our mission.",
